node.text: Happy 2023 from Kovalam! 😍🌴☀️ 🌊💓 Surprised my baby boy on New Year’s and my heart is so full! Already feeling the vibrant & colourful energy that this year has to bring in! Stay excited, stay in love & just trust it! - always! 🫶🏻😘🫶🏻
